One of my favorite beers ever. Rich, intense coffee aroma, and full body. Not too hoppy, with a fantastic chocolate background to the coffee. 

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone

Great Imperial IPA and the creamy mouthfeel from the lactose sugar sets it apart. Smells like a milky IPA. Great beer. 

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone

A delicious, balanced Stout. The cocoa and spice is pretty subdued, but evened out perfectly by the hops. Nothing overpowering. A nice, solid, drinking stout. 

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone

A decent lager. Nice aroma and a solid lager taste. A good drinking beer that I would have again.

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone
